   - Loading, empty ("All caught up!"), error, and due-count states
   - "Start Review" button → navigates to review session
   - "Back to Dashboard" navigation

3. **`apps/extension/src/popup/components/ReviewSession.tsx`** (new) — Full review session UI:
   - Displays word, pronunciation, part of speech
   - "Reveal Answer" toggle to show meaning
   - 4 rating buttons (Again/Hard/Good/Easy) with keyboard shortcuts (1-4, Space)
   - Progress bar, completion summary with time and rating breakdown
   - Loading, empty, error, and completed states

4. **`apps/extension/src/popup/App.tsx`** (modified) — Added `pendingReviews` and `reviewSession` views to routing

5. **`apps/extension/src/popup/components/PopupDashboard.tsx`** (modified):
   - "Start Review" now navigates to inline `pendingReviews` view instead of opening `options.html#review`
   - `reviewDue` count computed from actual vocabulary/review data via `getDueCount()`
   - DashboardCard and action button both show the accurate computed count

